{"tid":1091941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇靚女係唔知自己靚架","createTime":"2019-04-04T12:46:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T15:28:22.000Z","uid":238361,"like":8,"dislike":104,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8140e5f44fcb2d6f59d2c26bef9a443e8fd135ce","tid":1091941,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:46:15.000Z","msg":"話說前排成班frd吹水 (包括個公認靚女)，講開學業，靚女話驚爛grade，然後另外一個女仔同靚女講：「你用美色，行過去叫professor俾靚grade你咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢句嘢少尷，不過大家都認同咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等睇靚女有咩反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知個靚女好真心咁講：「我冇美色架喎」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻dead air咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通我地由頭指落腳趾尾解釋佢有幾靚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個重點係大家睇得出佢好真心咁唔覺得自己靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令我不禁思考「有冇靚女係唔知自己靚架」<br />\n啫係上面講咁多，我剩係想引申呢個問題出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求解答，勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：有識過靚女係唔知自己靚嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：全部識嘅靚女都知自己靚嘅"},{"pid":"84da18a4f053acdce63a9c94b9a99194464be5ae","tid":1091941,"uid":145460,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:47:29.000Z","msg":"冇圖你話你老母靚都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea34953c9392afdc17dfb16301b4ae765e09b30","tid":1091941,"uid":78613,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T12:47:31.000Z","msg":"就連唔靚果d都當自己靚..."},{"pid":"97deb8de8763a090b9b607715a242817ae82e1a1","tid":1091941,"uid":238361,"like":1,"d